Lebih Mudah Akses Web Api Dengan Postman Dan Hoppscotch

==========================================

Link nya : https://www.postman.com/downloads/?utm_source=postman-home
link nya : https://hoppscotch.io/

==============================

link json nya : https://catfact.ninja/fact

============================

buat code simpel nya :

index.html

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cat Fact</title>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <h1 id="fact"></h1>

    <script>
        $.get('https://catfact.ninja/fact', function (data) {
            // Display the cat fact on the page
            $('#fact').text(data.fact);
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>

===============================================
